title: The reason for regional Australia's women drought
text:

Merv Hall and Billy Hackett lament the fact that men outnumber women in Junee over beers at the Commercial Hotel. "You don't get Junee women because nearly everybody is related ... so you've got to be very careful about who you meet," the 63-year-old divorcee says.   The Age.
